{"tid":2054143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，今日起我會做YouTube負評師，利用AI力量杯葛中國企業","createTime":"2020-06-07T02:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T00:55:23.000Z","uid":159913,"like":113,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"98aac834d68c4159525da81fe0c62c1e149cab45","tid":2054143,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"淘寶開箱片? click入去負評 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4Z5icq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4Z5icq.gif&h=784fb9fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n小米手機review? click入去負評 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4Z5icq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4Z5icq.gif&h=784fb9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人講騰訊新game? click入去負評 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4Z5icq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4Z5icq.gif&h=784fb9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸節目/電影trailer? click入去負評 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4Z5icq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4Z5icq.gif&h=784fb9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解要俾負評?</strong><br />\n因為YouTube AI algorithm決定咗一條片如果負評比例較高，之後出現喺其他人嘅推薦影片嘅機會就會急跌，View數就會大大減少 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zTBpTN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zTBpTN.gif&h=70f1f1d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多YouTube頻道成日講中國產品，幫佢做免費宣傳<br />\n但中國ban咗YouTube，憑咩中國牌子可以上YouTube搵人宣傳?<br />\n所以我哋要堵塞呢個漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>會唔會影響到YouTuber? </strong><br />\n會但唔好意思，你promote中國產品我就係唔鍾意，所以要負評你 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42iYDdZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42iYDdZ.gif&h=0d038b1f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n明嘅YouTuber會發現多咗人負評關於中國嘅片，唔需要特別講原因 (留言會增加影片熱度)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由今日起我會成為負評師，每次順手一click送終國一程 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2gO0rn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2gO0rn.gif&h=a7fa4826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔駛專登搵嚟撳，只要見到就撳，醒起就撳，融入平時上開嘅網站根本冇得輸，0成本長做長有 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K30PKUa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK30PKUa.gif&h=a617cb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗YouTube仲有其他網站可以click負評，要靠大家諗諗咩地方可以加落去  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFNiDfm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFNiDfm.gif&h=4ec58003&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nYouTube<br />\nReddit<br />\nGoogle Play Store<br />\nApple App Store<br />\nIMDB"},{"pid":"bd31aa789615801e4714bd19602548176a399076","tid":2054143,"uid":259611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefaed36fe75e32cdfbddffd05e86ce71d731b41","tid":2054143,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"你幫紅企做宣傳老子就是不爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2068a71ee1050b4a6b24a291c4b72f311f6cdce9","tid":2054143,"uid":53062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"要用bot做先有用<br />\n一日幾千段片，你做得幾多"},{"pid":"b75f488a9b45d1aab61669151ca63a03d8c17d3b","tid":2054143,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"Join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4fb8f9d09aa474c78eb3db0228f50c51b75271","tid":2054143,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2068a71ee1050b4a6b24a291c4b72f311f6cdce9","tid":2054143,"uid":53062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"要用bot做先有用<br />\n一日幾千段片，你做得幾多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"用Bot好快俾人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防Vote manipul